      "text": "Harry Roberts was born on 14 June 2000 in the Allegemeines Krankenhaus in Viersen, North-Rhine Westphalia, Germany",
      "paragraph_ref": "12",
      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E003",
      "type": "FACTUAL_FINDING",
      "text": "It is alleged that at the time of his birth, Harry suffered an acute profound hypoxic brain injury",
      "paragraph_ref": "12",
      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E004",
      "type": "FACTUAL_FINDING",
      "text": "The central allegation is that she ought to have sought the assistance of hospital doctors at a much earlier point",
      "paragraph_ref": "14",
      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E005",
      "type": "LEGAL_FINDING",
      "text": "The first defendant admits that Midwife Clelland was its employee, it denies that it was vicariously liable for any failings on her part",
      "paragraph_ref": "17",
      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E006",
      "type": "FACTUAL_FINDING",
      "text": "Proceedings were issued in the High Court in London on 31 December 2004",
      "paragraph_ref": "15",
      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E007",
      "type": "FACTUAL_FINDING",
      "text": "The second defendant, who in fact indemnifies them, argues that liability is that of the first defendant.",
      "paragraph_ref": "16",
      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E008",
      "type": "FACTUAL_FINDING",
      "text": "The British military hospitals in Germany were originally set up to provide routine secondary care for British forces",
      "paragraph_ref": "39",
      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E009",
      "type": "EXPERT_TESTIMONY",
      "text": "Mr Branscombe said it was implicit that whilst working in the German hospital and in the German system the English midwives would have to work under the direction of the German system",
      "paragraph_ref": "51",
      "speaker": "Expert testimony"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E010",
      "type": "WITNESS_STATEMENT",
      "text": "Mrs Roberts states that eight months after his birth, therefore, in February 2001 he was reassessed.",
      "paragraph_ref": "90",
      "speaker": "Mrs Roberts"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E011",
      "type": "LEGAL_FINDING",
      "text": "There is no limitation defence under German law available to the defendants, given that Harry acquired knowledge in about June 2003",
      "paragraph_ref": "374",
      "speaker": "Judge's conclusion"
    },
